==English==
===Etymology===
Named after [[w:John Loudon McAdam|John Loudon McAdam]], who invented the process of [[macadamization]]. [[Category:English eponyms]]
Used for describing road surfaces originally constructed using the McAdam method, but now sometimes used for any road or street.

